episodes.title: Cult life - it's not for everybody (or anybody)
episodes.description:
Growing up in a cult is not a regular life. How do you escape? How do you start  new life? How do you grow after leaving?

Tune in and listen in as Martha Kartaoui shares her journey.



Want to create live streams like this? StreamYard is my absolute favorite live streaming platform. I've been using it since the beginning. Check out StreamYard here: https://streamyard.com/pal/d/5716014188724224
